 #What's Vaster?
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Vaster is a RTL->CA model converter.
 It reads VerilogHDL RTL model and creates SystemC CA model .


 #How to Build from sorce code?
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Download Vaster and Sister.
 
 Vister:https://sourceforge.net/projects/vaster
 Sister:https://sourceforge.net/projects/sister

 Build the sister.
 
 >> cd sister/src
 >> ./configure [options]
 >> make 
 
 Please enter the source directory and type as follows on your command line.

 >> cd vaster/src
 >> ./configure [options]
 >> make SISTER_DIR=../../sister


 #How to install?
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Please type as follows on your command line after build.
 
 >> make intall


 #How to use Vaster?
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 After installation, please type as follows.

 >> vaster [options] verilogHDL-files ...
        options :
            --help : displaying help.
            etc ...



--
end

